    Start program through menu or command line: gftp&
    Select "FTP" from toolbar
    Select "Options"
    Select "SSH" tab

        gftp FTP Options for SSH 

    Select "Apply" amd "Ok"
    On the upper rigt hand side of the gftp window, select "SSH" from the pull-down menu.

